>Ensign</cite> or <cite>Liahona,</cite> May 2006, 71.</p></li><li data-marker=15. id=note15><p data-aid=141537377 id=note15_p1><a class=scripture-ref data-old-href="../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.html?verse=6#p6" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.6?lang=eng#p6">Doctrine and Covenants 88:6</a>.</p></li><li data-marker=16. id=note16><p data-aid=141537379 id=note16_p1><a class=scripture-ref data-old-href="../../../scriptures/nt/col/1.html?verse=20#p20" href="/scriptures/nt/col/1.20?lang=eng#p20">Colossians 1:20</a>; see also <a class=scripture-ref data-old-href="../../../scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.html?verse=18-20#p18" href="/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.18-20?lang=eng#p18">2 Corinthians 5:18–20</a>.</p></li></ol></footer></div></article><div class=startHandle-2o_6p touch-action=none></div><div class=endHandle-wg4Dv touch-action=none></div></div></section></section><div class=mobileNav-1qobD><a class="mobileIcon-3ABLr mobilePrev-1Jf8d" href="/study/ensign/2019/11/43uchtdorf?lang=eng"><button dir=ltr class="iconButton--V5Iv navButton-WGhZC"><span class=hiddenTitleText-2SahY></span><svg style=width:1.625rem;height:1.625rem viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg role=presentation> <path fill=currentColor d="M4.438 10.856a.77.77 0 0 1 .097-.117l6.709-6.71a.755.755 0 0 1 1.065-.003.751.751 0 0 1-.005 1.064L6.6 10.795h11.647c.403 0 .744.335.744.75 0 .417-.333.75-.744.75H6.565l5.74 5.739a.755.755 0 0 1 .004 1.065.751.751 0 0 1-1.065-.005l-6.71-6.709a.757.757 0 0 1-.127-.169.755.755 0 0 1-.416-.671c0-.31.184-.574.447-.689z"> </path></svg></button></a><a class="mobileIcon-3ABLr mobileNext-1J33m" href="/study/ensign/2019/11/45stevenson?lang=eng"><button style=transform:scale(-1) class="iconButton--V5Iv navButton-WGhZC"><span class=hiddenTitleText-2SahY></span><svg style=width:1.625rem;height:1.625rem viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg role=presentation> <path fill=currentColor d="M4.438 10.856a.77.77 0 0 1 .097-.117l6.709-6.71a.755.755 0 0 1 1.065-